---
title: Saucy BBQ Striploin Steak with Loaded Brussels and Potato
description: Steak and potatoes get a serious upgrade in this dish. The striploin is transformed by BBQ seasoning and finished off with HelloFresh BBQ Sauce. Roasted Brussels sprouts and potato wedges are loaded with salty bacon, chives and cheddar cheese for an unforgettable steak night in!
